name: Sticker Maker Sticker Pack
summary: A WASTICKERS file is a sticker pack created by several mobile apps, including Viko & Co. Sticker maker and Sticker Maker Studio, specializing in WhatsApp Messenger stickers. It contains multiple .WEBP stickers, as well as a .PNG icon that represents the sticker pack in WhatsApp. WASTICKERS files also contain .TXT files that list the pack's author and title.
